漫威演员肯尼思·米切尔去世，享年 49 岁https://www.nme.com/news/film/marvel-actor-kenneth-mitchell-dies-ged-49-3592857?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=marvel-actor-kenneth-mitchell-dies-ged-49Sam Warner Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:58:07 +0000 Film NewsNews..MarvelMarvel Cinematic Universe https://www.nme.com/?p=3592857 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肯尼思·米切尔" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位演员因 ALS 并发症去世</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/marvel-actor-kenneth-mitchell-dies-aged-49-3592857">漫威演员肯尼思·米切尔去世后，享年 49 岁，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肯尼思·米切尔" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kenneth-Mitchell-2017-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/star-trek"><em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">星际迷航</em></a>演员肯尼思·米切尔去世，享年 49 岁。</p><p>周末，他的家人宣布了这位演员因肌萎缩侧索硬化症（ALS）并发症去世的消息。</p><p>他们在一份声明中表示：“我们怀着沉重的心情宣布肯尼思·亚历山大·米切尔去世，他是我们敬爱的父亲、丈夫、兄弟、叔叔、儿子和亲爱的朋友。”</p><p>他们补充道：“五年半以来，肯面临着 ALS 带来的一系列可怕挑战。以最真实的肯时尚，他成功地以优雅和承诺超越了每一个人，在每一刻都过着充实而快乐的生活。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3wkUg9tOmj/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.85